message: The flag of FLNKS, an extreme left-wing party, which is not the Kanak flag at all, is by no means the flag of New Caledonia : its raising is not provided for by any text with legal value. To present it in this way alongside the French flag is therefore a violation of the principle of neutrality. I therefore call for the removal of this flag, the only one that is official in New Caledonia being that of the Republic. /* The only official flag is that of France. */ new section
The flag of FLNKS, an extreme left-wing party, is not the flag of New Caledonia: it is not official (no legal text mentions it).
It is not the flag of New Caledonia, but the flag of FLNKS, a far-left party.

This flag is not the flag of New Caledonia, nor is it the Kanak flag. It is that of an extreme left-wing party, the FLNKS, known for having carried out armed attacks.  It is not official on the island, as it is not provided for in any legal text.
FLNKS flag is not official, it is the flag of a far-left party, and not the New Caledonia or Kanak flag.
